definitions.definition: A Romance language spoken in Occitania , a region of Europe that includes Southern France, Auvergne , Limousin , and some parts of Catalonia and Italy .

main_definition: A Romance language spoken in Occitania , a region of Europe that includes Southern France, Auvergne , Limousin , and some parts of Catalonia and Italy .

definitions.definition: Someone of the regional culture that speaks this language; an inhabitant of Occitania .

main_definition: Someone of the regional culture that speaks this language; an inhabitant of Occitania .
